### P-10: Progressive Disclosure for Timeline on Mobile

**Problem:** All 4 timeline steps are fully expanded on mobile. Each step shows number + title + full description = ~205px per step = ~820px total. On desktop, the alternating left-right layout with images creates visual variety. On mobile, it's four identical text blocks stacked vertically.

**Recommended approach:** Accordion pattern — show title + step number, tap to expand description:

```
Mobile (collapsed):
┌──────────────────────────┐
│ 01  Request a Quote    ▼ │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 02  We Assess          ▼ │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 03  We Clean           ▼ │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 04  You Walk Through   ▼ │
└──────────────────────────┘

Mobile (step 1 expanded):
┌──────────────────────────┐
│ 01  Request a Quote    ▲ │
│                          │
│ Submit our form or call  │
│ directly. We review the  │
│ request quickly...       │
│                          │
│ ⚡ Fast intake           │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 02  We Assess          ▼ │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 03  We Clean           ▼ │
├──────────────────────────┤
│ 04  You Walk Through   ▼ │
└──────────────────────────┘
```

**Implementation:**
```tsx
const [expandedStep, setExpandedStep] = useState<string | null>("01"); // First open by default

// In TimelineStep, on mobile:
<div className="md:hidden">
  <button onClick={() => setExpandedStep(
    expandedStep === step.number ? null : step.number
  )}>
    <span>{step.number}</span>
    <span>{step.title}</span>
    <span>{expandedStep === step.number ? "▲" : "▼"}</span>
  </button>
  <div className={`overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ${
    expandedStep === step.number ? "max-h-40 opacity-100" : "max-h-0 opacity-0"
  }`}>
    <p>{step.body}</p>
  </div>
</div>

// Keep full desktop layout:
<div className="hidden md:block">
  {/* existing desktop layout */}
</div>
```

**Impact:** Reduces from ~820px to ~280px (collapsed) with interactive expansion. Users engage with the content they care about.

**Effort:** Medium (3–4 hours). Dual layout (mobile accordion + desktop full).

