| `#2563EB` (royal) | `#FAFAF8` (warm) | **4.6:1** | ✅ Barely passes | Section kickers on light backgrounds |

**Fixes:**
- Gold on navy: Lighten gold to `#D4B85E` (bumps to ~5.0:1) OR use gold only for decorative elements (dots, lines) and switch text kickers to `#E2C868` on dark backgrounds
- Footer text: Change `text-slate-500` to `text-slate-400` on footer dark background
- Gold dots used as decoration (not text) are exempt from contrast requirements

